This is a small demo showing how you can sync video and a map using HTML5 and a wee bit of JavaScript. 

There's a full explanation on the Mozilla hacks blog:

http://hacks.mozilla.org/2010/12/spirit-of-indiana-jones-syncing-html5-video-with-maps

This can be improved a lot and I might do so soon:

- Open Street Map instead of Google
- Static map and Canvas path instead of Google maps
- Curved path
... (insert your idea here)